snippet.title: Paradise Island - VR MMO
snippet.description:
Now available on Steam! 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/400250

More an Experience than a Game, "Paradise Island" is a heavenly game in which you'll explore wonderful environments and places. The inspiration for the environments comes from the Renzo Piano designs and from the book "Origins of Achitectural Pleasure" in which the player's welfare is of primary importance.
